pedia.org\/wiki\/Wandering_Jew\" title=\"Wandering Jew\">Wandering Jew<\/a>. As a moralist, he used religious motifs and figures from the <a href=\"http:\/\/en.wikipedia.org\/wiki\/Christianity\" title=\"Christianity\">Christian<\/a> tradition without following the doctrines of the <a href=\"http:\/\/en.wikipedia.org\/wiki\/Christian_Church\" title=\"Christian Church\">church<\/a>.<\/p>","name":"P\u00e4r Lagerkvist","place_of_birth":"V\u00e4xj\u00f6 ,  Sweden","place_of_death":"Stockholm ,  Sweden","text":"P\u00e4r Lagerkvist , Literature, 1951","year":1951.0}